    "title": "[Suggestion] Use a decreasing difficulty depending on the time from last block to smooth the time between blocks",
    "body": "There would be a base difficulty which would work like the actual difficulty.\nAnd there would be a decreasing coefficient to reduce the variance.\nTake an example with a base difficulty of 100:\nWhen the last block is 5min old, the network would not accept a block with a difficulty less than 200\nWhen the last block is 10min old, the network would not accept a block with a difficulty less than 100\nWhen the last block is 15min old, the network would not accept a block with a difficulty less than 50\n\nCan someone confirm if this looks correct or would it break everything?\n",
